# Recflow Quality Subflow

Reusable final quality gate imported by the parent cockpit flow.

```yaml workflow
resources:
  - path: scripts/quality-check.sh
    kind: script
stateSchema:
  version: 1
  shape:
    quality: object
sequence:
  - node:
      id: qualityCheck
      type: script
      script:
        language: sh
        file: scripts/quality-check.sh
      writes:
        - /quality
```
